Document.Title: VMware Workstation 5.x: Sample config.ini File; CPU Speed Issue;http://vmware.com/info?id=97

Content:
;Evidently an upgrade can cause this file to go blank.

;This file is located at %AllUsersProfile%\Application Data\VMware\

;This one is for an Intel SpeedStep CPU at 1.66Ghz:
host.cpukHz = "1665000"
host.noTSC = "TRUE"
ptsc.noTSC = "TRUE"
